query: SELECT COUNT(*) as total, MIN(YEAR(entryDate)) as minYear, MAX(YEAR(exitDate)) as maxYear, COUNT(CASE WHEN YEAR(exitDate) < 2024 THEN 1 END) as before2024, COUNT(CASE WHEN YEAR(exitDate) >= 2024 THEN 1 END) as from2024 FROM trades;
